I Get Money I-I Get Money I-I Get I Get I Get I Get (Remix!!! AHHHHHHHH!!!!)

The Bentley the Ferrari, maybe the Bugatti

Nigga I don't walk nowhere I'm four wheelin

HO!!! HEY!!! (I, I Get It) HO!!! HEY!!! (I, I Get It)
